{
#----------------------------------------
# SAVE BACKUP TO FTP SERVER BY foisfabio.it
# 
# Script:  Save Backup FTP SERVER
# Version: 1.0
# RouterOS v.7.9.2
# Created: 14/11/2023
# Updated: --/--/----
# Author:  Fois Fabio
# Editor: Fois Fabio
